Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:14.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be on our way then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:17.96,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip. Cheer them all on for all of us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:18.53,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.46,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:24.37,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.71,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:30.62,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be terrible if I don't go to Minami's big game!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:34.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what kind of terrible things could happen if I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:35.63,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:33.13,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:40.75,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you do remember that you promised to stay home today so you wouldn't disrupt the game, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.61,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that, Kosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:46.31,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do that crazy thing you just said, I'll tell Keigo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:51.38,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ok, ok! Don't tell my dad! I'll do as I said and stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:53.45,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, then, I won't tell Keigo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:55.03,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:57.62,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love you, Kosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:58.74,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:04.55,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, if Keigo-san were to come back, it would mean a lot to Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:10.49,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keigo-san said that he was going to be coming back with the former manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:14.86,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he had something really important to say to onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:16.52,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it’s about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.45,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if it’s about onii-chan not being able to stay here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:22.41,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't just about onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:27.42,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If things don't go well for Kaoru-san... If her exam goes badly, she might have to go back to Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.89,0:01:29.47,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same with Minami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:33.82,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she were to get into a school far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:36.92,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to see her every day like I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:43.03,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy is staying with us in Sazanami for as long as she takes to heal, that’s what Mayu-onee-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:46.78,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means someday, I’ll have to say goodbye to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:55.69,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu-onee-chan, Kaede-chan, Yuuhi-chan, Hayu-onee-chan... We can’t stay together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:57.92,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:04.93,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a child, I hated winter. The blowing snow and the cold winds, I hate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:09.25,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate winter. Because it tells me that I’ll have to say goodbye to loved ones soon…
