Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:47.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.31,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time's running out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan... You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:17.83,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ima-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:27.73,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.48,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.16,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.07,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.98,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Okamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:52.41,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,53 to 54! B-Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.01,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:01.73,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We finally did it! We won! We beat Rikako-san and her gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:03.68,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:08.46,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what’s wrong? I really wanted to win against Rikako-san, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:09.26,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.31,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:15.34,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a great shot! You've gotten pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:19.30,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all... I'm still just a beginner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:22.88,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... It's not good for the new team captain to talk that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:23.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:27.73,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't give me 'huh'! You were chosen by unanimous vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.27,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't have you sniveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:33.76,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't! There really are better people than me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:39.54,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okamoto! I have full confidence in you. You can trust my judgment. I'm leaving the basketball team to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.12,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.68,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I can finally retire from the club with a clear conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.86,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Okamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.69,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:56.39,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woah, now, you really are sensitive. You're starting to get me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.60,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.45,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok, I get it, you can stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.96,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.60,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem really emotional, Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:29.68,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just hate sad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.25,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you, Listy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:37.58,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't know about like or dislike, but I do know I don't like sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.98,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:48.13,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really love it at Sazanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:57.47,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone there is really kind. If I could have my way, I would stay with them forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:01.08,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...But, it just isn't possible, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:05.72,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someday everyone will have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:12.37,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think everything changes over time little-by-little, but that doesn't mean it's bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:13.92,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:18.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just as you said, Listy... But still... Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:27.58,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tears don't suit you, you know. I prefer it when you're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.50,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be separated from everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.25,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want everything to stay just like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.85,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Looks like it's started to snow, Keigo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:52.10,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it certainly is as cold as it looks, but don't you love a White Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.06,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I certainly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.78,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:55.45,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.91,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we dawdle we'll keep everyone waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.52,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no worries. Sometimes it’s more fun the longer you put it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.66,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll return to Sazanami after you're finished with your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:06.77,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.20,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let's get a move on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:09.51,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.20,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.08,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.29,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:20.75,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're as white as a sheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.87,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t make a big deal out of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:30.00,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy... Did you take too much medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.93,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't because of that. It’s because of bath battle-mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.48,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Battle-mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.00,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.16,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s not your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:44.42,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's always been like this. I still struggle with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:46.57,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:53.71,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.44,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.45,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit here and watch you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:02.12,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if there's something I can do to help then I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:03.07,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:05.60,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:24.87,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:26.95,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:42.76,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika... Chika...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.11,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika... It's dirty there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:08:59.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:33.11,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.40,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no... Let it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.47,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.73,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing up so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.26,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.98,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.67,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.68,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:00.83,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:01.93,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.77,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No means no! It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:04.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes me wanna see it even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:05.34,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.01,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.15,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.98,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.00,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep... It's everyone's favorite foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone likes so many different things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.37,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I figured if I put it down in a notebook it would be easier to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:22.25,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is very detailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.11,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I like to write so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you really have been protecting all of your memories of us, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.72,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait? Last meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:36.62,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fs23\bord1.5\shad0.5\3c&H000000&}Since this will probably be my last meal at Sazanami, I want it to be something everyone will always remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:40.23,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Kanna-san comes back are you not going to be the manager anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.02,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to have to leave? If that happens, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.59,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just a temporary replacement for Kanna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s not that I want to leave, I’ll miss you all terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.57,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.65,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:55.44,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm not the manager anymore that doesn't mean I can't come around now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:58.95,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:07.04,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, how about you, Kanna-san and Keigo-san all be the manager at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.62,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I think it's a good idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.14,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:19.79,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.11,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.41,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A present!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:31.68,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A present?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.26,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep. A Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.18,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy! Have a look inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:45.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Memory Reader!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:46.72,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.40,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.95,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the opposite! Mayuki... How did you know I wanted this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:56.02,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can tell by looking at you... You're just like Chika used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:56.39,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.13,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to get some work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.10,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you both at the Christmas party later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.00,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:03.76,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:08.54,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously, thank you for this. I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:09.93,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.38,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you guys later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:16.46,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuki really is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.04,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.77,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn’t have powers like ours, but she can tell how we feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:21.97,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:27.10,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think it’s possible that everyone on Earth possesses some sort of secret power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.32,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:31.99,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.47,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the same as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.34,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,LC-20, hand over the TE-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:57.19,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver Ray, there are no serial numbers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:05.65,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that Silver Ray looks just like you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:11.94,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.10,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do this anymore... I can't take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:28.94,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may not like it, but there's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.30,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because we're not normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:37.79,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you try to leave, you'll just be chased down and imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:38.88,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.66,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really think there are those that would accept us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.98,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone like that just doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.82,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where we belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.52,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have nowhere else but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:52.48,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even still, I want to go! Someplace that isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.29,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, just become another doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.88,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver Ray, please just leave Listy alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:42.84,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:47.52,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,LC-20. Give it up and hand over the TE-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:50.32,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If not, you forfeit your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.64,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.59,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to Mayuki's present!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.78,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance. Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:09.98,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She’s insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.09,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:13.74,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's ok. I'll protect you, Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:19.83,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think you'll get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:30.64,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superb... Silver Ray is hunting down LC-20.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.01,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just think, when I get my hands on the TE-1,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.63,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what kind of fantastic creatures will I be able to bring forth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.66,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I think I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:54.92,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.18,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:56.93,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.96,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's out there waiting. If I don't do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:01.31,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:05.45,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,LC-20, TE-1, come out. I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:07.24,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.10,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.72,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.17,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, Silver Ray, come get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.63,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too weak! You think you can take me out with that attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:38.66,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,LC-20, stop running and fight. I've had enough of chasing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.95,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to get her as far away from Chika as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:47.69,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:53.15,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are creatures created like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.12,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, they are my little sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:55.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:02.67,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were born... no, created in a lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:09.81,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were all created to have abilities, to be used as weapons and deployed to battlefields. Trained to be killing machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:17.20,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Africa, Timor, Burundi, South-East Asia... We were sent everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.98,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was until someone from an organization tried to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:24.97,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that Keigo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:30.90,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they wanted me to help them counter other living weapons similar to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.22,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Counter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:38.99,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Keigo wanted me to protect you. But you got involved anyway. I'm sorry it turned out like this because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:39.85,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,LC-20, this is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.46,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:31.10,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,TE-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:43.40,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this power? Where is it coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:46.79,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver Ray, I can't let you take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.13,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it means my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:59.69,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kosuke, Mayuki, Minami, Kaoru, Izayoi, Mio, Kaede, Yuuhi, Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.83,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to stay with you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:19.58,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, Listy! That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:24.02,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika, this isn't a person! She's just a living weapon sent here to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:28.49,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not right! She is a person just like you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:30.53,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can feel the sadness in her heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.00,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're different from your kind, Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:35.26,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:39.24,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl is crying on the inside, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:40.79,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:43.18,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did you say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:43.82,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:45.33,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you're sad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:49.60,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you want to be with everyone, right? Didn't you say you didn't want to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:50.79,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:52.02,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,LC-20...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:54.73,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:56.92,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's your mission, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:57.56,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:59.38,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:05.17,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to keep on living! It might hurt at times when people ignore you or treat you badly, but someday you'll feel happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:09.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll meet people who will make you happy. You can make that your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:11.68,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You blind optimist...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:14.09,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,LC-20, hurry up and give me peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:15.84,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:19.25,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That there’s no point in my living anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:20.35,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:21.99,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:28.01,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, Listy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:42.83,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.78,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,TE-1, why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:53.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who you are or how you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:57.21,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone has the right to be happy, and you shouldn't give up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.88,0:24:00.49,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we're together, I know we can be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:02.83,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Listy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:04.25,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:07.46,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:13.25,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright then, Chika, come outside with your big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:25.05,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chika...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:45.29,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver Ray, what happened? Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.33,0:24:47.02,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.86,0:24:53.68,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryu Hakue of Ryukikan organization, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.30,0:24:58.41,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest for human trafficking, genetic manipulation, and other illegal activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.18,0:24:59.87,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.76,0:25:10.45,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m fine with being a dog. It’s better than controlling people's hearts and bending them to your will!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.43,0:25:16.95,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.01,0:25:19.08,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.18,0:25:24.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver Ray is still alive, but you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.62,0:25:29.03,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silver Ray won't hurt anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.78,0:25:33.81,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... Okay... Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.11,0:25:35.01,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can consider this case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.63,0:25:38.17,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy, looks like we'll make that Christmas party after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.63,0:25:39.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.38,0:25:43.32,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.06,0:25:46.33,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok, shall we head over?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.59,0:25:46.98,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.67,0:26:03.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.50,0:26:08.90,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you guys are all riled up and excited, I, Nimura Mayuki, will sing a song for you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.30,0:26:13.90,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuki, are you sure you’re okay? I mean, there’s your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.16,0:26:16.36,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was concerned about that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.48,0:26:19.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut your faces! How dare you make me remember something I was finally able to forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.89,0:26:21.90,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don’t take it out on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.93,0:26:24.59,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly, we’re just trying to be considerate...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.59,0:26:26.09,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re EVIL, I say. Evil!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.10,0:26:28.10,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayu-onee-chan, that’s not very ladylike of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.10,0:26:28.90,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut your face! Uh oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.30,0:26:29.96,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.65,0:26:31.29,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.87,0:26:33.73,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the getup? You going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.17,0:26:34.99,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kosuke-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.99,0:26:37.27,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.81,0:26:40.74,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought if I left before you noticed, it would be easier on you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.97,0:26:42.13,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.53,0:26:43.42,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.97,0:26:46.71,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanna-san is back, so I think this part-time job is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.16,0:26:51.69,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may have only been for a short time, but I'm so glad I met you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.87,0:26:55.12,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I truly won't forget our time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.77,0:27:01.12,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Speaking of which, Kanna-san I've been putting this together since I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.45,0:27:02.84,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, please use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.12,0:27:13.44,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Kosuke-chan, it looks like I really did pick the right person for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.37,0:27:15.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! You can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.11,0:27:17.84,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.99,0:27:21.12,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From now on, you'll be the full-time manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.45,0:27:22.89,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please keep up the good work, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.21,0:27:25.72,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep up the... what are you doing, Kanna-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.96,0:27:27.53,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me? Well, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.55,0:27:29.44,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.58,0:27:34.61,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to become Keigo-san's wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.92,0:27:39.64,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.66,0:27:43.06,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanna-san, Keigo-san, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.06,0:27:43.73,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.18,0:27:46.52,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you were going to get married, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.89,0:27:49.55,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's to Keigo-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.73,0:27:51.03,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.10,0:27:52.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mio-chan, congratulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.74,0:27:54.22,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.70,0:27:55.80,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well it's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.85,0:27:58.22,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great Mio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.53,0:28:00.37,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful mother you now have!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.49,0:28:01.07,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.47,0:28:04.55,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanna is Kanna! Kanna ain't Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.89,0:28:07.49,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't that Mama Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.60,0:28:10.85,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that isn't the point, Minami! That’s not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.93,0:28:13.41,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's my little Mio-baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.83,0:28:16.71,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Let go! You're creeping me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.98,0:28:17.26,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a cute daughter I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.32,0:28:19.30,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.01,0:28:21.82,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.81,0:28:23.53,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.89,0:28:28.24,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mission is over, I guess it's time for me to hit the road, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.09,0:28:31.00,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.23,0:28:35.58,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never felt like this before. I want to face my mission head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.95,0:28:36.83,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m happy for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.20,0:28:37.75,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.84,0:28:40.24,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like you finally found a place where you truly belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.69,0:28:42.70,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you can feel at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.94,0:28:44.93,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.74,0:28:49.00,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to return somewhere, it should be home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.36,0:28:50.15,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.48,0:28:55.10,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there are people here who will say "welcome home," then this is where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.91,0:28:59.64,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.79,0:29:05.90,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!  We can stay together forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.66,0:29:10.75,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! To celebrate, I, Shiina Yuuhi, shall now sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.95,0:29:14.04,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I sing with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.09,0:29:14.66,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.68,0:29:15.81,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.06,0:29:17.05,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.10,0:33:13.54,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The place where, even if you're away a long time, where everyone says "Welcome Home" with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.80,0:33:17.17,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the place I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.25,0:33:21.07,THSJ Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
